      • psxy

        public static java.lang.String psxy(Symbol symbol,
                                    double symbolSize,
                                    HorizontalPosition position,
                                    double value,
                                    java.nio.file.Path colorPalletPath,
                                    java.lang.String... additionalOptions)
        パラメータ:
        symbol - type of marking
        symbolSize - size of symbols
        position - on the map
        value - of plotting
        colorPalletPath - Path of a color pallet
        additionalOptions - if any options
        戻り値:
        echo latitude longitude value | psxy -V -: -J -R -P -K -O symbol [additional] >> $psname

      • psxy

        public static java.lang.String psxy(HorizontalPosition start,
                                    HorizontalPosition end,
                                    java.lang.String... additionalOptions)
        Draw a line from start to end
        パラメータ:
        start - start position of the line
        end - end position of the line
        additionalOptions - any other options
        戻り値:
        psxy -V -: -J -R -P -K -O [additional] >> $psname

      • psscale

        public static java.lang.String psscale(java.lang.String name,
                                       double interval,
                                       double xpos,
                                       double ypos,
                                       double length,
                                       double width,
                                       java.nio.file.Path cptPath,
                                       java.lang.String... additionalOptions)
        パラメータ:
        name - of scale
        interval - of tics
        xpos - x position of edge
        ypos - y position of edge
        length - of scale
        width - of scale
        cptPath - Path of pallet
        additionalOptions - if any
        戻り値:
        psxy -V -K -O -P -Bname -Dxpos/ypos/length/width(h) -CcptPath >> $psname

      • psCoast

        public static java.lang.String psCoast(java.lang.String... additionalOptions)
        If you want to fill dry areas, then -Gcolor (e.g. -Gbrown)
        パラメータ:
        additionalOptions - if any the return will have them. ex) National boundaries -N1
        戻り値:
        pscoast -J -R -Bs -Dc -V -W -K -O (additional) >> $psname
